<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/feb/06/">&#x27a0;</a> February 6, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="please-raise-my-taxes-nytimesc" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/06/opinion/06hastings.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss&amp;pagewanted=all">Please Raise My Taxes - NYTimes.com</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>This is exactly my attitude (which I refer to as &#8220;left-wing capitalism&#8221;). People should be free to earn as much money as they can, but an increasing amount of it should be taxed.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
