<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/dec/11/">&#x27a0;</a> December 11, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="nobel-physicist-chosen-be-ener" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/12/10/AR2008121003681.html">Nobel Physicist Chosen To Be Energy Secretary</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Yes, I know it&#8217;s still the honeymoon period, and Obama isn&#8217;t even president yet, but still… His appointment of a Nobel Prize-winning scientist who has been researching renewable energy to the post of Secretary of Energy is such a great sign.  Really excited for the next four years.</p>

