<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/nov/04/">&#x27a0;</a> November 4, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="john-mccains-concession-speech" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.johnmccain.com/Informing/News/Speeches/Read.aspx?guid=6d126e21-5857-40c3-96e2-4f504e27e22c">John McCain&#39;s concession speech</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>A genuinely gracious and powerful speech.  &#8220;I urge all Americans who supported me to join me in not just congratulating him, but offering our next president our good will and earnest effort to find ways to come together, to find the necessary compromises, to bridge our differences, and help restore our prosperity, defend our security in a dangerous world, and leave our children and grandchildren a stronger, better country than we inherited.&#8221;</p>

