    <div class="well" id="gop-tickets-appalling-contempt" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.slate.com/id/2203120">The GOP ticket&#39;s appalling contempt for science and learning. - By Christopher Hitchens</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;This is what the Republican Party has done to us this year: It has placed within reach of the Oval Office a woman who is a religious fanatic and a proud, boastful ignoramus.&#8221;  I love Hitchens.</p>

