<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/oct/23/">&#x27a0;</a> October 23, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Ten Years in My Life: US Immigration Status</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2968947660/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Ten Years in My Life: US Immigration Status" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3004/2968947660_65847fcf93_m.jpg" height="240" width="237" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>On Saturday, 24th October 1998, I flew from Glasgow to Boston, with little more than a suitcase of clothes and a credit card with a decently high limit.</p>

<p>It's now 24th October 2008.  Ten years have gone by.  Time for little personal retrospection.  How have I spent these ten years?</p>
        </p>

